Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽叫你去和爸爸告別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是能觸摸到本人的最後機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撫摸他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷冰冰的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子澆下去的話 爸爸會喊冷的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸已經…
