Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有信送來了 放你桌子上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:32.70,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,580)\pos(232,479)}終天的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:32.70,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,580)\fs30}{\pos(320,419)}Eternal Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道Death啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎 六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學？沒聽說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道你和她吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凸守啦 凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道吃了黑暗羊蹄根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰沒事跑去啃樹根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 說的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個髮型是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我覺得雙馬尾有點孩子氣 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長 忍住！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你嘴裡說出來總覺得很彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請放手 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮可是少女的生命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便玩弄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…從那以後我也考慮了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人…不 小鳥遊學姐的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和學姐說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐她…茴香學姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個美少女是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 五月七日同學 眼睛怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒仍算尚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只要飲用此物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啊啦 那身打扮 真是奇葩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:10.78,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛Death啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙 難道是國中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑烈火使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼 看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦～別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀…話說 你為什麼要模仿六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是傳承 師從邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳承？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 最終的無月之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她把一切黑暗力量託付於吾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換而言之 吾為邪王真眼繼承者！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西不要去繼承啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑烈火使仍未消亡 邪王真眼就必須長存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是六花說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…有點帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是哪種模式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣收拾完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回頭想想 其實也沒幹過什麼正事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 戲劇社那邊怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入了喔 姑且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 社長十分熱血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整天喊「表演出屬於自己的角色吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我們將會開創新紀元」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 確實有這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 熱血其實挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:07:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挺好 但是他的話聽著感覺像中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真的是中二病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能跟中二病有點區別…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己是與眾不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己發現了新事物就認為自己是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就被這個觀念束縛著拼命標新立異
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你和我都從中二病畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要過普通的高中生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這也只是堅信自己是普通高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後再次被這個設定所束縛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是到頭來 人身上總有一些「病」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好啦 我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做菜又要摔壞餐具了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我有那麼笨手笨腳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道小鳥遊姐姐不在 你很寂寞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她又不是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你還不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚搬家公司過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是去一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,末班車不到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.99,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(618,123)\frz4.471}收到簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.99,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(648,270)\frz6.329}新簡訊 1條
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.99,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(828,396)\frz7.413}無主題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和爺爺奶奶都很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼做 讓她們很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我認為這樣是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太也這麼覺得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果全都是我的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她摘下眼罩也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她從中二病畢業也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.07,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,267)}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.08,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fad(100,0)\pos(603,231)\frz7.751}勇氣之友 勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Flame…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當汝閱讀此信之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汝恐怕已非漆黑烈火使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據2012瑪雅預言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,籠罩世界的毀滅波動會吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的精神波會遭受弱化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會變得豁達 放棄目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退化成只享受眼前所見之物的愚蠢凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如今能感受到那種苗頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以寫下此信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑烈火使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別被假像蒙騙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擁有力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是被黑暗之王「邪王」所選中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非他人 你是特殊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中二的時候 給兩年後的自己寫的信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼嘛 太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近娛樂中心的遊戲幣也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去用吧 這種時間你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去接六花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想對她說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想為她做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑烈火使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾 第二代邪王真眼 有訊息傳達於你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 爸爸死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全沒有實感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法感受到任何情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直以為爸爸很快就會康復
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到爸爸去世的早晨 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那時 我遇到了勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給我？六花說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 小六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 邪王真眼早在兩年前就與你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在她來到女教皇住處之時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爺爺讓我們跟他一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛…喂 啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空氣有些許黏著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 就在…附近！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此 每天都看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵 這下終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰正在監視我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:14:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小六花覺得 能擁有這種幻想真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比抑制自己的感情 對人言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更加率真 帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她…她的中二病是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小六花是被中二病所拯救的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是看著你地陶醉於中二病 憧憬著率真的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是被你的力量所吸引 想模仿你的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才選中了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非你不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小六花 一直…一直一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要澆水了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾非「勇太」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 邪王真眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有東西想給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,定下契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊 小偷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.72,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆 叫警察
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花 過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是選擇回到無聊的現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是選擇跟我一起改變現實？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀 色狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 演罪犯 演罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我摸一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住 別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去Death吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓凸守家開車送我們過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要換人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 只要使用漆黑烈火使的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那只是輪船的燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單純的燈光…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是黑暗之力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馳騁吧 具現於世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,崩裂吧 融入吾軀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vanishment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This World！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是不可視境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那道光正在注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳達吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直沒說出口的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a&HAF\3a&HAF}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都會說中二病很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不想回想起來 甚至想要把記憶消除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個時候奇特的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的已經消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄想著自己被誰監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,設定自己的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並完全融入的過去的自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人有時會口吐狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妄想著突然改變的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像著遙遠的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在腦裡描繪天馬行空般的恢宏愛情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事從出生到入土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人類中永無止境地輪迴著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永無止境不斷重復著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷 害羞 惹人愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名為自我意識過剩的「病」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在薈薈眾生中彰顯「自我」的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 人的一生就是一場中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼 看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:21:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是中二病
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.39,0:22:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是太害羞了
